    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a limited-slip M Differential Lock for optimal torque distribution. Mechanically flawless, this M3 has received proactive rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension architecture remains tight with refreshed bushings and OEM dampers, ensuring the legendary 50/50 weight distribution is fully realized. Finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather, the interior maintains its factory matte finish with no bolster fatigue. A meticulously documented, turn-key example for the purist collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
