    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This vehicle has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one, and it shows. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from swirl marks, stone chips, or any imperfections; it has been treated with a multi-layer ceramic coating to ensure its continued brilliance. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state. The premium leather upholstery still carries that distinct 'new car' aroma, with absolutely no bolster wear or creasing on the seats. Every button, switch, and digital interface functions with the tactile precision of a vehicle fresh off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It features a comprehensive service history with oil changes performed every 3,000 miles regardless of use. The engine bay is immaculate, showing no signs of heat cycling or fluid seepage. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule. Included are all original keys, the window sticker, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, your search ends here.",
      "price": 48500.0,
